N2  - The article presents an update on the Academy of Management as of June 1966. A meeting was held by the Eastern Division of the Academy of Management on May 13 and 14 at the University of Maryland in College Park, Maryland. The Eastern Division has voted to have its 1967 meeting at Harvard University. The annual meeting of the Midwest Division of the Academy of Management was held at the University of Kentucky.
