N2  - The article comments on the dilemma facing students of administration when evaluating whether any corporate effort is well administered. Asking the question reveals the signs of development in the field of study and practice of administration. The author comments that students of business administration are becoming increasingly open to new theories and conversations about administration. An overview of the upcoming October and December 1966 issues of the ?Academy of Management Journal? is also presented.
