N2  - The purpose of this article is to bring together a summary of research on motivation of scientists and engineers in combination with data from interviews with ten scientists and engineers in a large research and development laboratory. Those interviewed were managers, who functioned on various levels. In order to present this summary, the device of a hypothetical clinical study of one George Engineer was chosen.
